This directory contains all the files you need in order to run Echidna on tempest, the main server of the Virginia Tech Particle Astrophysics group.
1) Copy echidna.cfg and pbs_echidna.sh to offline/Echidna
2) Copy Makefile_echidna to offline/Echidna and rename it Makefile
3) Copy modules/* to offline/Echidna/modules/
4) Run make in offline/Echidna
At that point, you should be able to run Echidna locally.